steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"9fb8a","text":"Make this solution up as a SINGLE stock solution.  For 1L of stock solution,","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"h2h","text":"* Start with ~600mL de-ionised water.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"fsf8i","text":"* Weigh out and dissolve each component (except ferric chloride and citric acid) directly in the 600mL solution.  Allow each to dissolve completely before adding the next.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"3krm4","text":"* For the KOH, add pellets slowly, a few at a time, with constant mixing.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"fmn8f","text":"* Dissolve the citric acid separately in 100mL de-ionised water.  Dissolve the ferric chloride 6-hydrate directly in the citric acid solution.  Stir the ferric chloride-citrate solution for 15 minutes, then add slowly to the main stock solution while stirring.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"iobs","text":"* Make up to 1L.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"bsu4i","text":"For 1L of stock solution, dissolve the calcium nitrate 4-hydrate directly in 700mL de-ionised water.  Make up to 1L.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"bs0m9","text":"For 1L of stock solution, dissolve the magnesium sulfate 7-hydrate in 700mL de-ionised water.  Make up to 1L.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"cqh9s","text":"(Optional): For 1L of stock solution, dissolve 4.50g sodium metasilicate 9-hydrate in 700mL de-ionised water.  Make up to 1L.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"3qpka","text":"The sodium metasilicate can also be weighed out and dissolved directly in the growth medium at the time of preparation.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ba28","text":"For 100L of 1× hydroponics solution:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"7l417","text":"* Prepare ~90L of water.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"3ahak","text":"* Mix in 100mL of each stock solution, mixing well before adding next stock solution.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"21ho4","text":"* Add sodium metasilicate 9-hydrate (0.00450g/L) and dissolve with stirring, if not done as solution D.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"8e58h","text":"* Adjust pH to 5.5","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"6on10","text":"* Dispense to growth trays.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"73f91","text":"Monitor and adjust pH of stock solution daily at pH 5.5 with KOH/HCl as required.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"v1t6","text":"Refresh stock solution twice per week.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}
